        "body": "Elastic search reindexing of pull requests is continuing. All data is preserved, but may not be available on pages relying on elasticsearch until the reindex is complete.<br /><br />Pages and APIs that do not rely on elasticsearch, including the GitHub CLI (gh pr list) and API (/repos/{owner}/{repo}/pulls), are not impacted and can be used to retrieve pull request data in the interim.",
